Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.20,0:01:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了五月 有什麼可以採收的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.10,0:01:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…紅蘿蔔、蕪菁、韭菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.11,0:01:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有草莓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.85,0:01:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於到時候了 好期待喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.79,0:01:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 好期待哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.16,0:01:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.22,0:01:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 都已經四月了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.13,0:01:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天卻有點冷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.79,0:01:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳先回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.36,0:01:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也馬上就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.43,0:01:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.87,0:01:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子也餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.87,0:02:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣 先回去做飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.74,0:02:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那天在學校見過慊人之後經過了幾天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.85,0:02:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過由希依然很開朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午餐要煮什麼好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.57,0:02:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 這該不會是十二生肖裡的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.58,0:02:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.48,0:02:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}音同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.59,0:02:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服裡面好像有東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.06,0:02:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽的 肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.53,0:03:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透應該馬上就回來了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.23,0:03:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 你來做點東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 阿夾 我看先這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.41,0:03:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就先把菜挑好 等他們回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.28,0:03:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 就算無聊也別這樣搞我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.01,0:03:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能這樣浪費食物喔 阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.52,0:03:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰理你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.95,0:03:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 回來了…咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.62,0:03:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上剝了這條蛇的皮 弄個燒烤來吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.36,0:03:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾…綾女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.30,0:03:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是綾女嗎 怎麼突然來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上剝了他的皮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.97,0:03:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 別激動 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.84,0:03:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩綾女 就像你所看到的他是條蛇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.21,0:03:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是綾女…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.35,0:03:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他睡一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.51,0:03:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛇不是會冬眠嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.02,0:03:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是這樣 綾女也很怕冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.52,0:03:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像今天這種冷天很容易就會變身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.12,0:04:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾女跟我和波鳥同年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.66,0:04:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小學、國中到高中一直都在一起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.00,0:04:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說 三個人在一起就成了花般耀眼三人組了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣呀 原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 什麼花般耀眼三人組啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼前浮現波鳥痛苦的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.11,0:04:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 剛才由希為什麼那麼生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在是煩死人了 我連提都不想提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.94,0:04:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂 不可以這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.64,0:04:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.48,0:04:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對自己的親哥哥這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.42,0:04:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.59,0:04:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥…哥哥…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.53,0:04:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就由我自己來說明吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我身體凍僵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在尋找暖身的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.63,0:04:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時正好有人過來 就不知不覺的跟著對方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.64,0:04:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想這就是所謂的本能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.81,0:04:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 還有我親愛的弟弟 過得好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.88,0:04:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像長大後的由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不知不覺嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.82,0:05:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該慶幸還好沒被抓進警察局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.25,0:05:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 他對妳做了什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.69,0:05:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 夾竹桃你也在這裡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.76,0:05:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少這樣叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先不管夾竹桃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.46,0:05:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見啦 紫吳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.54,0:05:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在的期間 你沒有拈花惹草吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.68,0:05:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有你在 我哪可能做那種事呢 綾女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.81,0:05:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.58,0:05:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.82,0:05:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來和由希的個性不太一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹 她就是本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.96,0:05:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是來找她的對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.06,0:05:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真是失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.27,0:05:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是由希的親哥哥綾女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.87,0:05:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 初次見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.14,0:05:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此…原來如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.81,0:05:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的像女王一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.68,0:06:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這邋遢男人窩中唯一的一朵花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.78,0:06:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像被困住的女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可沒困住她喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.82,0:06:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥 你別捉弄人家行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.09,0:06:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太失禮了 我可是很尊敬她喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.09,0:06:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女王 首先給我一杯茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午餐也快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡尊敬呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.70,0:06:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真難伺候呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.10,0:06:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.10,0:06:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 我們去外面吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.67,0:06:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.97,0:06:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好考慮的 我請客！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.71,0:06:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我生氣也沒用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.01,0:06:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 儘管點妳喜歡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.05,0:06:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便 我要水餃定食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.19,0:06:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用掛意由希他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.36,0:06:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是小孩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.53,0:06:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們會自己弄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.39,0:06:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我一直受他們照顧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.40,0:06:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都說要請客了 難道妳不捧場嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.37,0:06:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全沒這回事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.17,0:06:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆 給我兩份水餃定食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.61,0:07:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.44,0:07:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都他決定了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.24,0:07:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過真讓人驚訝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.35,0:07:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希從來沒說過他有哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.01,0:07:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒說過你是十二生肖的一員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.78,0:07:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒說是理所當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.32,0:07:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就如妳所看到的 我們的感情不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.76,0:07:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 應該說是不親吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年紀也差了10歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希一出生又因為有病在身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因而被隔離了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔離？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.50,0:07:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也有不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.84,0:07:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於這個弟弟的存在總是毫不在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.21,0:07:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直按著自己的方式撫育他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我發現問題時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.38,0:07:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間已有很深的代溝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.59,0:07:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希在學校時不是碰到了慊人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳當時也在場吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.22,0:07:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詳情我也很難說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.89,0:07:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之對由希來說 慊人是個可怕的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.10,0:08:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想他現在一定很消沉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.90,0:08:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是來見妳 但應該說是來看由希的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.74,0:08:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果發現他還挺有精神的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.31,0:08:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說心裡鬆了一口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.51,0:08:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說我不是個好哥哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.68,0:08:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於你們之間的代溝 你後悔嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.32,0:08:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的是 人隨著年齡的增長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.32,0:08:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小時候不懂的事慢慢就會了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.96,0:08:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時應該這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.60,0:08:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時應該這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.27,0:08:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢都會了解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.43,0:08:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我與其說是後悔 倒不如說是懺悔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.17,0:08:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許是想藉著懺悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.31,0:08:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去否認自己以前的年幼無知吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 所以人家都說大人很自私吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.35,0:08:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽曾經這麼說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.42,0:08:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要等到自己為人父母才開始了解天下父母心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.46,0:09:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.16,0:09:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是其實最該了解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.36,0:09:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最不可以忘記的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小時候的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.27,0:09:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次學會吊單槓的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.61,0:09:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次被罵得很慘的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.51,0:09:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有孩提時候感受到的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.51,0:09:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠好好的記住的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.28,0:09:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算長大成人也能夠互相理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便無法完全做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.55,0:09:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少也能靠近那種心境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.05,0:09:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這種想法會讓人比較快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.23,0:09:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想說的只是…也就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.07,0:09:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和由希今後一定會有所進展的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.41,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.08,0:09:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得真是好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.69,0:10:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 我媽媽是宇宙最棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.42,0:10:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我說的是妳啦…算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.59,0:10:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.50,0:10:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白由希為什麼那麼有精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.17,0:10:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我和由希才要開始嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也努力看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.54,0:10:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後也請妳繼續做由希的好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.55,0:10:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時的綾女…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.12,0:10:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 大家午餐吃了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.55,0:10:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是我哥哥有沒有困擾妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.66,0:10:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 還請我吃水餃定食呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.16,0:10:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你討厭你哥哥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.94,0:10:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是問問而已 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是討厭…應該是難搞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.84,0:11:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我實在不知道他在想些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.61,0:11:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難搞的話 好好克服就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.35,0:11:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是我們親近的時候 弟弟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.86,0:11:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一離開店面後 天氣突然又冷起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.89,0:11:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以又變回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說要是太冷的話 蛇會死掉的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.60,0:11:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫我是蛇嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.06,0:11:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才不是我哥哥 我跟你沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.57,0:11:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實是無法改變的！由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.30,0:11:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們回來了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.71,0:11:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 由希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.78,0:11:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時的綾女流露了哥哥的微笑喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.52,0:11:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳 今晚我睡哪兒呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？你要住下來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.38,0:12:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續睡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.15,0:12:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.42,0:12:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是不得已的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.66,0:12:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為由希把門鎖上不讓我進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.03,0:12:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你去紫吳的房間睡嘛 就像昨天那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.86,0:12:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但紫吳不讓我跟他睡嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.50,0:12:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 兒童不宜耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.20,0:12:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.54,0:12:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要待到什麼時候呀\N不聽！不聞！不問！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈…不必傷腦筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.21,0:12:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我要睡小透那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.31,0:12:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾回去！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.18,0:12:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾女來後第三天的早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.45,0:12:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但和弟弟由希的代溝卻似乎愈來愈深了..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 綾女來了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.16,0:12:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從過年後就沒再見過他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去找他好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.50,0:13:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但會打擾到他們兄弟團聚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.90,0:13:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希怎麼樣？高興嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.44,0:13:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.61,0:13:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希生病了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.55,0:13:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.22,0:13:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但綾女是店長 放著店面不管好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.26,0:13:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？綾女在開店嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.73,0:13:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是賣一些護士、空姐、女僕等的服飾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是洋裝店嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.54,0:13:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾女說是一間販賣男人夢想的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 你們很厲害唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.04,0:13:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.64,0:13:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.58,0:13:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.78,0:13:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就從學校回來 那麼想跟我說話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒很想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.32,0:13:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.09,0:13:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獨處呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是擔心這個才趕回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.79,0:14:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在看什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.59,0:14:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們以前高中時期的相簿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.30,0:14:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看 波鳥也在呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.60,0:14:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳和波鳥都很年輕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.50,0:14:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾女也和現在的由希好像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.14,0:14:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有朝氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.41,0:14:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.04,0:14:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾女從這時起就留長髮了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 雖然違反校規
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.69,0:14:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 你也看一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.79,0:14:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是了解你哥哥的絕好機會喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.03,0:14:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是非要我說明為何學校允許我留長髮了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.26,0:14:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.80,0:14:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 就在入學後不久…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.74,0:14:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有天我突然被校長叫住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.24,0:14:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本是自己想說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.17,0:14:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,髮色雖然允許了 但我可沒說可以留長髮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天以前去把它剪掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.21,0:14:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,校長 我是王族的後代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.88,0:14:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都沒告訴別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.55,0:15:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我有天得回到我的國家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.02,0:15:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說為何我們王族非留長髮不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.79,0:15:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說第一代國王魯魯巴拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.12,0:15:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在滿四歲時曾接受神的告誡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.83,0:15:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四方放著刺有金與紅光的卡多拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.26,0:15:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當頌為馬魯多穆尼的卡多拉額上出現青光時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.20,0:15:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯巴拉的身體就彷彿鞭策過的駿馬般得到解放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.94,0:15:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨著滿懷的慈愛 頭髮如沐春風般飄逸起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.38,0:15:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在這時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說到眾所周知的卡司巴魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.35,0:15:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本已如帶芽的花般在御所安息著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.32,0:15:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪知胸部突然發出卡巴尼魯的高鳴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.72,0:15:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等…對不起…我待會還有會面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.06,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡多拉的事我還沒說完呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.16,0:15:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 要留長髮就留吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.90,0:15:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣才可以留長髮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是王族的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是胡說的囉 豬頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好懷念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.71,0:16:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那再講一個你不敢相信的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾女可是學生會長喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.45,0:16:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別耍寶了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.25,0:16:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之總會有人看著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.59,0:16:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟史無前例的綾女的行為總是引人注目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.19,0:16:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是校規 活動等也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了綾女那一代後變得頗具變化而有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.63,0:16:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為他真的有實力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.17,0:16:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我倒認為波鳥比我更適合當學生會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.40,0:16:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.61,0:16:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢業旅行那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.74,0:16:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能忘記呢 綾女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.64,0:16:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.35,0:16:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這好像可以讓由希對綾女產生興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.39,0:16:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是縮短彼此距離的機會 綾女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.89,0:16:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 當時呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.76,0:16:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有部份學生在旅行中涉足了聲色場所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.93,0:16:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸 先別急著罵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.17,0:17:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體健康的男人誰都會想進去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.57,0:17:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們可沒去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.31,0:17:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為已不是稀奇事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.78,0:17:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得還真輕鬆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.48,0:17:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不幸地是 這件事被老師知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.95,0:17:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.42,0:17:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們全部被告知會遭到退學的處分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.02,0:17:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然身為學生會長的我也提出了抗議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.16,0:17:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在學生 家長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.86,0:17:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,校長與老師之間進行了協調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.56,0:17:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們雖然未成年卻涉足聲色場所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.60,0:17:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的行為當然不足以為取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.27,0:17:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有法律就得遵守 否則秩序將會大亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.14,0:17:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但將性慾這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.51,0:17:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當作是壞事般的全盤否定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.11,0:17:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對此點感到相當遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.65,0:17:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為許多人揹負著傳宗接代的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.65,0:17:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我認為性慾是擔任此使命的一端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.39,0:17:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有那麼可恥 罪惡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.79,0:17:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.59,0:17:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的綾女比平常還認真呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常的他果然只是裝瘋賣傻而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此我在這裡有個建議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.30,0:18:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這未成年的尷尬年紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.50,0:18:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該拯救這群無處發洩慾望的年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.01,0:18:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後請把各位的慾望發洩在我身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.51,0:18:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為學生代表的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.51,0:18:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承擔大家的慾望也是理所當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.38,0:18:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且對男學生的家長來說這樣也比較放心安全吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.65,0:18:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 盡情發洩你們的慾望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.56,0:18:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若以接受與攻擊來比喻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.56,0:18:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是接受者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.69,0:18:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是豬頭呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.53,0:18:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然腦筋有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是無可救藥的白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.29,0:18:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈 不需要多慮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.40,0:18:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然像我這樣子 不過我可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.36,0:18:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這件偉大的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.57,0:18:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看是蠢事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.60,0:18:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太失禮了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.54,0:18:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這樣 所以大家都免於遭到退學呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.24,0:18:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為波鳥後來幫忙擦屁股囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後就這樣 到畢業都是綾女當會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.68,0:18:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.81,0:18:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？由希 對哥哥是否有點了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.35,0:18:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代溝 代溝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.12,0:18:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.75,0:18:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就來講理事長銅像的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 你出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.42,0:19:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是某個夏日的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.72,0:19:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.33,0:19:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳 想想辦法解決這傢伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.29,0:19:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？不是挺愉快的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.49,0:19:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對呀 很愉快呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.36,0:19:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很痛苦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.86,0:19:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我對他也沒轍 唯一有用的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.14,0:19:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 門沒鎖 我就進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.84,0:19:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是波鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.94,0:19:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥 怎麼突然來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.31,0:19:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潑春要我帶你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.62,0:19:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此為止 打道回府如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.32,0:19:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.86,0:19:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很吵 好像也沒時間輕鬆地聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你最吵嘛\N但我會再來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.73,0:19:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.73,0:19:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳 後會有期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有空我會去你那邊走走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.01,0:19:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥 你是走來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.34,0:19:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 開車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了表示歉意 我來開車吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.41,0:19:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.28,0:20:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾女從以前就最聽波鳥的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說他很崇拜波鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.02,0:20:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說波鳥擁有他所想要卻沒有的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以很崇拜波鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.56,0:20:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說很想珍惜他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.63,0:20:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前他們也常說正經事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.73,0:20:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以波鳥可說是綾女的保姆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.94,0:20:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 真是麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.88,0:20:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真這樣想的話 行動前先用用大腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.88,0:20:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.15,0:20:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是由希還是不願打開心胸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.18,0:20:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希也不是傻瓜 只是年紀還小罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.02,0:20:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多事情不願讓步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好心急的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.19,0:20:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透和你有點像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.23,0:20:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老是為別人著想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.63,0:20:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拼命的專注起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.03,0:20:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是對這樣的人沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.84,0:20:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.11,0:21:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總能說些討人喜歡的話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.48,0:21:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾女說的話很有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.02,0:21:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是無可救藥的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.82,0:21:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代溝 代溝 代溝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.09,0:21:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但綾女…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.09,0:21:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.06,0:21:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於擁有自己所沒有的東西的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.99,0:21:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能坦然的表現出好感是很棒的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.63,0:21:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們應該能夠有所進展的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.37,0:21:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潑春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.68,0:21:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思讓你操心了 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.35,0:21:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣想不是比較愉快嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.79,0:21:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.52,0:21:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘了問他賣護士或女僕服飾到底是什麼店了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.03,0:21:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.16,0:21:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是色情俱樂部的話題嗎
